        "product_description": {
            "value": "Upgrade your kitchen prep with the ASR Outdoor FCB-2110 Thin Flexible Cutting Board Chopping Mat set. This 20-pack of lightweight, flexible cutting mats is designed to make food preparation faster, cleaner, and more convenient. The thin, bendable design allows you to easily funnel chopped ingredients directly into pots, pans, or bowls without spilling, making cleanup effortless. Each mat provides a smooth, durable surface ideal for cutting vegetables, fruits, meats, and more. Perfect for use at home, while camping, or on any outdoor adventure, these flexible boards store easily in tight spaces and take up minimal room in drawers, backpacks, or kitchen cabinets. The generous 20-pack ensures you always have a fresh, clean surface on hand and can dedicate separate mats to different food types to help reduce cross-contamination. Easy to rinse and quick to dry, these mats are a practical addition to any kitchen or camp kit. Lightweight, portable, and reliable, the ASR Outdoor flexible cutting mats deliver everyday convenience for cooks of all skill levels.",
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "ai",
